s in its perfect=\r\ned form, its nature, challenges it faces etc. \nStory of Lord Narasimha demo=\r\nnstrates how energy/drive in us operates in \nits perfected form, its nature=\r\n, challenges it faces etc. And so on.&lt;br&gt;&nbsp;&lt;br&gt;Our\n scriptures are not =\r\nfilled with meaningless stories. They are true \nstories of events in some o=\r\nther realms of being. They also \nmetaphorically represent great inner truth=\r\ns that may occur within us. \nThey can help us understand ourselves, how we =\r\ncan perfect various \naspects of our personalities and how we can progress.&lt;=\r\n/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div style=3D&quot;color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 13.3333px; font-f=\r\namily: arial,helvetica,sans-serif; background-color: transparent; font-styl=\r\ne: normal;&quot;&gt;&lt;span&gt;&nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div style=3D&quot;color: rgb(0, 0, 0); fon=\r\nt-size: 13.3333px; font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif; background-colo=\r\nr: transparent; font-style: normal;&quot;&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span&gt;*&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&=\r\nnbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; *&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; *&lt;br&gt;&nbsp;&lt;b=\r\nr&gt;&lt;/span&gt;Chanting a deity&#39;s name or doing other rituals to a deity, are the=\r\n first step. If a mantra is working, a corresponding aspect of our personal=\r\nity will become purified and perfected over time.&lt;br&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div styl=\r\ne=3D&quot;color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 13.3333px; font-family: arial,helvetic=\r\na,sans-serif; background-color: transparent; font-style: normal;&quot;&gt;&lt;span&gt;&nb=\r\nsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=3D&quot;yui_3_7_2_46_1367025215463_58&quot; style=3D&quot;c=\r\nolor:rgb(0, 0,\n 0);font-size:13px;font-family:arial, helvetica, clean, sans=\r\n-serif;background-color:transparent;font-style:normal;&quot;&gt;Best regards,&lt;br&gt;Na=\r\nrasimha&lt;br&gt;--------&lt;br&gt;Astrology &amp; Spirituality Resources: &lt;a rel=3D&quot;